---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout
  title="About Me"
  description="Learn more about Paweł Zentala, Developer Experience consultant, programmer, and innovation activist"
>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto p-4">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">About Me</h1>
    
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 mb-12">
      <div class="md:w-1/3">
        <img 
          src="/images/profile.jpg" 
          alt="Paweł Zentala" 
          class="rounded-lg shadow-md"
          onerror="this.src='https://via.placeholder.com/300x400?text=Paweł+Zentala'"
        />
      </div>
      
      <div class="md:w-2/3">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Paweł Zentala</h2>
        <p class="text-lg mb-4">
          I'm a Developer Experience consultant, programmer, and innovation activist.
        </p>
        
        <p class="mb-4">
          This site is a collection of my ideas and concepts across various domains of technology,
          business, and social innovation. I believe in sharing ideas openly to inspire others and
          potentially find collaborators.
        </p>
        
        <div class="mt-6">
          <a 
            href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/zentala/" 
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-primary text-white rounded-md hover:bg-primary/80 transition-colors"
          >
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433c-1.144 0-2.063-.926-2.063-2.065 0-1.138.92-2.063 2.063-2.063 1.14 0 2.064.925 2.064 2.063 0 1.139-.925 2.065-2.064 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"/>
            </svg>
            LinkedIn Profile
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">About This Site</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        This site serves as a personal collection of ideas that I've thought about over time.
        Think of it as a digital garden of concepts – some may be fully formed, others just seedlings.
      </p>
      
      <p class="mb-4">
        Each idea is presented as a card on the homepage. Click on any card to explore that idea in more detail.
        Some ideas have custom visual representations, while others use a standard format.
      </p>
      
      <p>
        Feel free to browse by tags if you're interested in specific areas or topics.
        If you'd like to discuss any of these ideas or collaborate, please reach out via LinkedIn.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</MainLayout>